# LearnGraph Coding Standards

## Monorepo Structure
- `apps/web` — Next.js 16 App Router application
- `packages/db` — Drizzle ORM schema and database client
- `packages/ai` — LLM orchestration (Vercel AI SDK) + ingestion pipeline (`src/ingestion/`)
- `packages/fsrs` — FSRS-5 spaced repetition engine
- `packages/shared` — Shared types, constants, utilities

## Tailwind v4
- All design tokens defined via `@theme` in `globals.css`
- NO `tailwind.config.ts` — Tailwind v4 is CSS-native
- Use CSS custom properties for colors (`:root` / `.dark`)
- Use `hsl(var(--token))` pattern for color values

## TypeScript
- Strict mode enabled everywhere
- All tRPC procedure inputs validated with Zod schemas
- Prefer `type` over `interface` for data shapes
- Export inferred types from Drizzle: `typeof table.$inferSelect`

## Components
- Built on shadcn/ui (New York style) + Radix primitives
- Every data-fetching component needs loading, error, and empty states
- Use `next-themes` for dark mode (class strategy)
- Font: Inter for UI, Source Serif 4 for AI mentor responses, JetBrains Mono for code

## Data Layer
- Drizzle ORM for schema definition and queries
- RLS policies in raw `.sql` migration files (not Drizzle)
- pgvector for embeddings (1536 dimensions)
- All tables have `created_at` timestamp with timezone

## AI & Ingestion
- Primary: Claude Sonnet 4.5 (teaching, summarization, concept extraction)
- Fallback: GPT-4.1-mini (flashcards, classification)
- Embeddings: text-embedding-3-small (1536 dims) via Vercel AI SDK `embedMany`
- All LLM calls use `generateObject` with Zod schema — never raw text completion
- Ingestion pipeline: `packages/ai/src/ingestion/pipeline.ts` orchestrates extract → chunk → embed + summarize + concepts
- Semantic chunking: headers → paragraphs → sentences, 512 max tokens, 100 overlap
- Concept dedup: canonical name match + embedding cosine similarity ≥ 0.92
- Toasts: `sonner` — import from `@/components/ui/sonner`
